      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic evaluation of turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model form uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty for both the k-omega SST turbulence closure and the Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model has not been assessed. Multiple model forms exist in literature; no sensitivity study conducted."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
