      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sensitivity analysis and uncertainty propagation for all material and boundary condition inputs.",
      "rationale": "Input sensitivity analysis not performed. Hemolysis model coefficients (C, alpha, beta) sourced from single literature study; variability in these parameters across studies is known but not propagated."
    },
    {
