      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative mapping of validation experiment input parameters to COU input parameters with equivalency bounds.",
      "rationale": "Porcine blood rheology used in validation differs from human blood rheology in COU. No formal equivalency analysis performed to bound the impact of this substitution on hemolysis predictions."
